originalText.text: After several attempts at the series 65,  and not succeeding, I switched to the 66, and found Matthew. Thank God! We worked hard, 3-4 days a week for 10 weeks. I took the test today and passed. I could not have done it without him. He was patient, caring, knowledgeable, reliable and strategic. I absolutely know, I would not have had the confidence or knowledge to pass without all his help. He is passionate about what he does and smart too! Thank you Matthew!!

originalText.text: Matthew is a superior tutor in every single aspect of his craft. He helped me pass the most daunting securities licensing exams, the Series 65 and 63. Frankly his devotion, dedication, and wisdom are the foundation of his excellence. He will make sure that when you walk into the room to take your test, you will be more prepared to not just pass it, but to absolutely obliterate whatever it is that they throw at you. His excellence has been crafted into a formula that will foster improvement in facets that you will see in real time. Matthew’s formula works and his wisdom is vast. His ability to know the answer to thousands of questions is staggering. His efficient approach will show you the result that you desire. If you are even considering taking your licensing exams look no further then Securities Prep LLC.
